# F1 Telemetry Dashboard

A modern Formula 1-inspired telemetry dashboard designed to visualize racing data in real time. The application provides race-engineering style insights including speed, throttle, brake pressure, steering angle, gear selection, tyre information, lap performance metrics, and vehicle status monitoring.

## Features

* Real-time telemetry visualization
* FIA-inspired dashboard interface
* Speed, RPM, gear, throttle and brake monitoring
* Steering input visualization
* Tyre temperature and wear tracking
* Lap timing and sector analysis
* Interactive charts and gauges
* Responsive web interface
* Three.js powered visual components

## Technology Stack

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript
* Node.js
* Three.js

## Purpose

This project was created to provide an immersive race-engineering experience for Formula racing enthusiasts, sim racers, and developers interested in motorsport telemetry visualization.
